jook

Objective:
Collect as much food as you can in 3 rounds.
Collect food and bring it back to your base.  Can only hold x amount of food at a time

Collect powerups to help you pick up more food then your opponents.
    Powerups:
        super speed
        bug traps



After each round, use your food to invest in ways to get more food
    collect
        insects that help you collect
    steal
        insects that steal from other players
    defend
        bug traps that keep stealing insects out


Strategically price investments according to their benefit




___________________________________
Bug movement
bug brings up to x items of food back to base
    each food counts towards score

